  Lines:
  - One last thing for you to learn is the upgrade system.
  - What's an idle game without progression, am I right?
  - All you need to do is gather some materials, then use the Upgrades menu. Each
    tier will consume the materials.
  - Go ahead and try upgrading your strength.
